What you need to know:

Odipo landed a life-changing scholarship to study and play football in the United States at Midcontinent University mid 2000He undertook his Doctorate in Business Administration Studies in Marketing and International Business and currently teaches in the Business Department at Shorter UniversityBesides teaching, Odipo, 46, runs his sports apparel company, Overcoming Adversity (OA) Limited, which manufactures playing kits